  <name>Segra</name>
  <summary>Record and clip your gameplay</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      Segra records your gameplay and lets you clip, highlight, and share it. It captures with OBS
      (libobs) using hardware encoders — NVENC on NVIDIA and VAAPI on AMD/Intel — and includes a replay
      buffer, automatic game detection, and a built-in clip editor.
    </p>
  </description>

